id: wear_amulet
title: "The Magical Amulet"

dialogue:
  - narrator: "You put on the amulet."
  - narrator: "Suddenly, you can understand the whispers of the forest."
  - narrator: "The trees seem to guide you toward your destination."
  - narrator: "With the amulet's power, you find your way home safely."
  - narrator: "But the forest never forgets those who wore the amulet..."

next: ending_magic
